# 💬 Realtime Chat Application

A **Realtime Chat Application** built with **Node.js, Express, MongoDB**, and **WebSockets**.  
This project allows users to register, login, and chat with each other instantly, similar to WhatsApp-style messaging.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🔐 **User Authentication** (Register & Login)
- 💬 **Realtime Messaging** using WebSockets
- 👤 **User-to-User Chats**
- 📱 **Responsive UI**

---
## 📂 Project Structure
    chat-app/
│── server.js # Entry point
│── package.json # Dependencies
│── config/ # DB & app config
│── models/ # Mongoose schemas
│── routes/ # Express routes
│── public/ # Frontend files (HTML, CSS, JS)
│── websocket/ # WebSocket handling

---
## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
- **Database:** MongoDB  
- **WebSocket Server:** External WebSocket integration  
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Other:** bcrypt (password hashing), JWT (authentication), etc  

